%% Diagram: CDC approach decision tree
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    Start([Need to propagate DB changes]) --> Q1{"DBA can grant<br/>logical replication slot /<br/>binlog reader?"}
    Q1 -->|Yes| LB[Log-based CDC<br/>Debezium / DMS / native]
    Q1 -->|No| Q2{"Can install<br/>AFTER triggers?"}
    Q2 -->|Yes| TR[Trigger-based CDC<br/>shadow table + relay]
    Q2 -->|No| Q3{"Hard deletes<br/>used on source?"}
    Q3 -->|No| PL[Polling-based CDC<br/>SELECT WHERE updated_at &gt; hwm]
    Q3 -->|Yes| AP[Application-level events<br/>or transactional outbox + log-based CDC]

    LB --> Q4{"Self-managed Kafka?"}
    Q4 -->|Yes| DZ[Debezium on Kafka Connect]
    Q4 -->|No, AWS-native sinks| DMS[AWS DMS]
    Q4 -->|No, SaaS, low ops| FT[Fivetran]

    classDef preferred fill:#f4fcf4,stroke:#2f9e44,color:#1f5f2c
    classDef caution fill:#fff8e6,stroke:#e67700,color:#704700
    classDef bad fill:#fff5f5,stroke:#c92a2a,color:#7a1f1f
    class LB,DZ,DMS,FT preferred
    class TR,PL caution
    class AP bad
